{"tid":1657161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好信話咩加泰警察好克制","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:27:23.000Z","uid":64131,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa2a8bbdc519cb2948fdb5648cf23b544de4e82","tid":1657161,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"見到呢幅圖facebook 勁多人share<br />\n但其實天下烏鴉一樣黑囉好無<br />\nfake news幫唔到手不特只<br />\n事後仲要浪費時間澄清架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9i7pkEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9i7pkEi.jpg&h=356d50bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n「歷史重演」<br />\n<br />\n昨天西班牙最高法院裁決加泰獨派領袖罪成後，引發支持者上街聲援政治犯，加泰境內各處都爆發群眾騷動。西班牙黑警晚上於巴塞隆拿國際機場，暴力驅散遊行並佔領當地的示威者，造成多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一位示威者遇擊致眼球爆裂，經診斷後醫生相信是被橡膠子彈射中眼部。另有一位示威者陰囊受傷，喪失一枚睪丸。<br />\n<br />\n根據加泰醫療網絡統計，昨晚加泰境內示威共有131名示威者、47名警察受傷，其中29人為重傷：6人被海綿彈擊中，5人頭部受撞擊，16人其他身體部位受創。傷者主要出現在巴塞機場。</span><br />\n<br />\nEl Nacional: Five strokes in the head, loss of an eye and a testicle: the balance of the police charges<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elnacional.cat/ca/politica/ferits-aeroport-protesta-sentencia-ull-testicle-porra-cap_430535_102.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elnacional.cat%2Fca%2Fpolitica%2Fferits-aeroport-protesta-sentencia-ull-testicle-porra-cap_430535_102.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=7486e364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elnacional.cat/ca/politica/ferits-aeroport-protesta-sentencia-ull-testicle-porra-cap_430535_102.html</a><br />\n<br />\nEl Nacional: The boy who was injured at the airport lost his eye<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elnacional.cat/ca/politica/sentencia-proces-perd-ull-noi-ferit-aeroport-prat_430430_102.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elnacional.cat%2Fca%2Fpolitica%2Fsentencia-proces-perd-ull-noi-ferit-aeroport-prat_430430_102.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPL